commit.message:
setup.py: Make dependencies installable via pip

Closes: https://github.com/rqlite/sqlalchemy-rqlite/pull/3

setup.py: fix sqlalchemy ImportError when called by pip

Load constants.py without importing __init__.py, since pip
calls setup.py before sqlalchemy is installed.

Reported-by: Kai Hildebrandt <kai.hildebrandt@uniberg.com>
